OL,3,CWelsh Ambulance Service declares
OL,4,C"critical incident"
OL,6,FThe Welsh Ambulance Service has
OL,7,Fdeclared a "critical incident" because
OL,8,Fof significantly increased demand
OL,9,Facross the 999 service and extensive
OL,10,Fhandover delays.
OL,12,FThe service says more than 340 calls
OL,13,Fwere waiting to be answered at the
OL,14,Ftime the critical incident was
OL,15,Fdeclared on Monday evening.
