OL,3,CWelsh Ambulance Service declares
OL,4,C"critical incident"
OL,6,FMore than half of the Trust's
OL,7,Fambulances were also waiting to hand
OL,8,Fover patients outside hospitals,
OL,9,Fleading to some people waiting "many
OL,10,Fhours" for an ambulance and staff
OL,11,Ftaking longer to answer calls.
OL,13,FThe service is urging the public to
OL,14,Fcall 999 only for serious emergencies.
OL,15,FThe Trust says it has taken additional
OL,16,Fmeasures to ensure it can continue to
OL,17,Fdeliver a service to the public.
