OL,3,CWelsh Ambulance Service declares
OL,4,C"critical incident"
OL,6,FStephen Sheldon, head of service,
OL,7,Fsaid: "It is very rare that we declare
OL,8,Fa critical incident, but with
OL,9,Fsignificant demand on our service and
OL,10,Fmore than 90 ambulances waiting to
OL,11,Fhand over patients outside of
OL,12,Fhospital, our ability to help patients
OL,13,Fhas been impacted.
OL,15,F"Regrettably, this means that some
OL,16,Fpatients will wait longer for an
OL,17,Fambulance to arrive and for their
OL,18,Fcalls to be answered. For that, we are
OL,19,Fvery sorry because this is not the
OL,20,Flevel of service we want to provide."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
